VariablesList.Remarks: Data for Total Triaxial UU/UNC Tests

Variable.Name: CBR
Variable.Text: 'Find the largest in each schedule:^dim max as single = 0.0^dim var25 as Clisp.Tests.variables^dim var50 as Clisp.Tests.variables^^for each sch as Clisp.Tests.Schedule in Specimen.Stages(1).Schedules^ var25 = sch.Variable("CBR25")^ var50 = sch.Variable("CBR50")^^ if (var25 is nothing) orelse (var50 is nothing) then^ 'ignore it!^ else^ if max | var25.Value then^ max = var25.Value^ end if^^ if max | var50.Value then^ max = var50.Value^ end if^ end if^next^^return max

Variable.Name: Preparation
Variable.Text: 0^'0=Static Compression with Tamping^'1=Static Compression in Layers^'2=Dynamic Rammer Compaction to a specified Density^'3=Dynamic Vibrating Compaction to a specified Density^'4=Dynamic Rammer Compaction with a specified effort^'5=Dynamic Vibrating Compaction with a specified effort^^^

Variable.Name: Time
Variable.Memo: Elapsed time since the start of data logging

Variable.Name: Stress
Variable.Text: dim d as single = PistonDiameter.Value * PistonDiameter.Value * 0.00785398^dim s as single = (Load.Value / d)^return (s / 100)

Variable.Name: AtInitialDisplacement
Variable.Text: 'The displacement level at the start of the engage:^dim eng as Clisp.Tests.Schedule = Stage.Schedules(Schedule.Index - 1)^dim iL as single = ipPenetration.StartValue(eng)^dim fL as single = ipPenetration.Value^^if (fL |= iL) then return 1^return 0
